            <title>[SPARK-3415] Using sys.stderr in pyspark results in error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3415</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using sys.stderr in pyspark results in: &lt;br/&gt;
